summary:
Hey guys! 
I’ve been away for a while! I finished my finals about a week and a half ago, but... i had a couple of personal...
body:
Hey guys!

I’ve been away for a while! I finished my finals about a week and a half ago, but… i had a couple of personal things (mostly mental health related) so i took a bit of a break from art, but now! I’m well rested and ready to go!

This is Becker, a character i created for my Human Anatomy final! I liked her design and i think i’ll explore her a little more haha

Hope you like it!
